[BIO-INTEL-2026-007] — Interoceptive Precision Enhancement (Pillar 7)

System: Embodiment / Body‑Brain Unity / Decision Architecture

Description:
High‑level cognition, moral reasoning, and self‑modeling depend on precise interoceptive signaling (insular cortex). Low precision degrades predictive coding, causing poor decisions and emotional dysregulation.

Core challenge: 👉 Amplifying visceral signal fidelity without causing anxiety, somatic amplification, or autonomic imbalance.

Failure Mode:
Predictive Coding Failure & Emotional Dysregulation.
Overweighted interoception ($w \to 1$) causes anxiety; underweighted ($w \to 0$) causes dissociation. Both degrade belief updating.

Physical Model:
Active inference: $FE = D_{KL}[Q(s)||P(s|o)] + \mathbb{E}_Q[-\ln P(o)]$
Interoceptive precision $\Pi_{int} \propto 1/\sigma_{visceral}^2$; optimal $w \approx 0.5$.

Limitations:

· Insular mapping coarse in fMRI.
· Heartbeat detection tasks lack ecological validity.
· taVNS causes systemic side effects.

Constraints:

· Non‑invasive targeting (insula deep).
· Autonomic balance maintenance.
· High individual variability.

Current Solutions:
Mindfulness, taVNS, biofeedback, propranolol/SSRIs.
→ Transient, low signal‑to‑noise, no structural enhancement.

Research Gap:
No validated epigenetic or neuromodulatory pathway that durably enhances insular‑PFC connectivity and interoceptive precision.

AI Opportunity:
Wearable autonomic decoding + closed‑loop taVNS/CRISPRa + Bayesian precision gating.

Proposed Directions (2026 Upgrade):

· Launch EWAS – scATAC‑seq of insular cortex from high‑precision vs. low‑precision subjects.
· Target insular‑PFC coupling, not just insula – strengthen mPFC→insula inhibitory pathway via HD‑tDCS before enhancing insula itself.
· Bayesian precision gating – dynamic adjustment of interoceptive weight $w$ based on task demands.
· taVNS as bridge – closed‑loop taVNS synchronised with insular EEG to drive Hebbian strengthening.
· Real‑time interoceptive precision index (IPI) – wearable ECG + HRV + respiratory sinus arrhythmia.

Impact Level: Critical – forms the biological substrate of wisdom, empathy, and intrinsic alignment.

